    "title": "simple-installer",
    "version": "1.2.0",
    "description": "Simple installer tool for any type of application, built with .NET Core. It has a very limited set of features, and is not intended to be a full-fledged installer. It has limited support for uninstalling, and is intended to be used for simple applications that do not require a lot of configuration and permissions."
